707232f-a.text:
Ave. W. east from East 3rd Street, showing in foreground No. 432, at the S.W. corner of East 4th Street and Ave. W., beyond it is the Police Training School of Brooklyn. At the left, is a row of 2-story houses numbering from back to foreground 441-455.
October 1928.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
